    "global_vars_data_operations_sync_detail": "For each child, global_vars and data_operations are identical in content. ParseCommand has both empty. PlaceOrder has three entries each. CancelOrder has three entries each. TrackOrder has one entry each.",
    "coverage_detail": "All three available data stores (orders, inventory, payments) are covered across the children. orders is accessed by PlaceOrder (write), CancelOrder (read_write), TrackOrder (read). inventory is accessed by PlaceOrder (write) and CancelOrder (write). payments is accessed by PlaceOrder (write) and CancelOrder (write).",
    "final_status": "ok"
